org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.catalog
Class AeCatalogMappings

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.catalog.AeCatalogMappings
public class AeCatalogMappings
extends java.lang.Object

Wraps the details of catalog xml file. It creates a AeCatalogBprMapping object for every entry in the catalog document. It also validates that the documents exist in the BPR file.
